# Makefile Commands Reference

## Environment Setup
- `make setup-dev` - Set up development environment from .env files
- `make setup-staging` - Set up staging environment from .env files  
- `make setup-prod` - Set up production environment from .env files
- `make setup-all` - Set up all environments

## Running Workflows
- `make run-rpa1-dev` - Run RPA1 in development mode
- `make run-rpa1-staging` - Run RPA1 in staging mode
- `make run-rpa1-prod` - Run RPA1 in production mode
- Similar patterns for RPA2 and RPA3

## Testing
- `make test` - Run all tests
- `make test-unit` - Run unit tests only
- `make test-integration` - Run integration tests only
- `make test-coverage` - Run tests with coverage report
- `make test-watch` - Run tests in watch mode

## Development
- `make install` - Install production dependencies
- `make install-dev` - Install development dependencies
- `make clean` - Clean up temporary files and caches
- `make lint` - Run linting with ruff
- `make format` - Format code with ruff

## Configuration
- `make list-config` - List current configurations
- `make info` - Show project information and available workflows